@patitonav You have probably figured this out a long time ago, but I'm posting some code here anyway in case someone else is also looking for the answer. Remember to replace `{PROJECT_NAME}` and `{TOPIC_NAME}` in the code below. 

```python
from googleapiclient.discovery import build

# Publisher.
service = build('pubsub', 'v1')
mytopic = 'projects/{PROJECT_NAME}/topics/{TOPIC_NAME}'
data = 'hello, world!'
service.projects().topics().publish(topic=mytopic, body={
      "messages":
        [{
         "data": base64.b64encode(data.encode('utf-8'))
        }]
    }).execute()
print("Published message.")
```

